{
  "id": "RAW_f4ff6f6b",
  "title": "会 24h 学习的 OpenClaw“小龙虾”，已经开始虾说虾唱了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5MTA3NzcxMQ==&mid=2247487956&idx=1&sn=8c61b7d8dc76a35385b9e13a24cc91b1",
  "date": "2026-03-09 03:07:00",
  "author": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "siteName": "MiniMax 稀宇科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed6cd012&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUqLjwjsK1PcRbEANRvLq6KbQ8HVicDBegy8kCNYjDRQPmBfu98mdmM3gxK7yialvBs3SxhToxBA4IPshGpAqiaic1mamKlEtzFzZMbjxkV07L4A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天给大家介绍两个让你的「小龙虾」拥有声线、学会唱歌的方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">我们将 MiniMax Speech 语音模型和 Music 音乐模型的开放平台接口进行了深度封装，并正式上架到了Openclaw 生态中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过在 Clawhub 中学习新 Skill，你的小龙虾不仅</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可以在</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">飞书</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">、企业微信、钉钉</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">等</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">I</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">M</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">中</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">拥有定制音色、语音回复消息，还</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能够创作完整歌曲、不同风格的纯音乐、以及人声哼唱的 demo，变成一个既会说话又会唱歌的全能 AI 搭子。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Voice Maker：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">clawhub.ai/BLUE-coconut/mm-voice-maker</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Music Maker：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">clawhub.ai/BLUE-coconut/mm-music-maker</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:10px 20px;z-index:1;margin:10px -30px 10px 0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:5px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;overflow:hidden;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1.25;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">虾虾能说会道</span></strong></p>\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">你的多语种配音专家</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们将文字转语音、音色设计等强大功能集合在了 Voice Maker 技能中。小龙虾通过学习并成功验证 MiniMax API Key 后，即可解锁“语言大师”身份。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它不仅内置了 40+ 种语言和近百种预置音色，还支持自动切分脚本，轻松搞定多重语音、多情感的段落配音。与此同时，我们将音色设计（Voice Design）功能也集成到了 Skill 中。你可以直接用自然语言描述心中想要的音色，实现对音色多维度的精准创造。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们做一个测试：在输入“选择一个你认为符合你性格特点的音色，用英文说一段自我介绍”的Query后，小龙虾为自己选择了一个“赛博少女”音色，设计了一段英文自我介绍并直接预览播放。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5138888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2940\" data-height=\"1510\" data-imgfileid=\"100004286\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7af4ab9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUqLjwjsK1PczDxxiaqtjjuOypLGr5Echexr0ONia8usH2IQt0vCxNoNL3N4754iaiacVmAuOkRsEwGVd9bo2qYB7kQWHMfHQ2uTDnkpA1TtGj0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Voice Maker 支持切分脚本并分配角色配音，按文本背景与人物属性匹配输出情绪。例如，我们请小龙虾制作一段奶奶和小泰迪熊的故事，可以在一段有声书音频中听到有奶奶、泰迪熊与旁白三种音色。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5740740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2932\" data-height=\"1684\" data-imgfileid=\"100004288\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d825bef2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUqLjwjsK1PdymMAmY8LJAcXBl0grtgxP505TgXmQF8BQsiaavfN5gmiarpt9icibkXcvvpYlObNCGANqVXemfrhY8HdQsRH5iaTPM1b83JKyDwjE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:10px 20px;z-index:1;margin:10px -30px 10px 0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:5px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;overflow:hidden;flex:100 100 0%;width:auto;height:auto;\">\n     <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size:36px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 5px 0px 2px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 2px solid rgb(240, 60, 22);padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;line-height:1.25;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">麦霸附体</span></strong></p>\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">全能音乐制作</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除了能说，你的小龙虾也可以当个麦霸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在学习了 Music Maker 技能并验证 API Key 后，小龙虾就拥有了音乐创作能力。无论是一首长达 5 分钟的完整流行音乐、一段用来放松的纯音乐，还是随口的一段哼唱旋律，它都能轻松拿捏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们在已和OpenClaw配对的飞书中发送指令，生成一首专注于办公学习的白噪音：</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">给定你想要的曲风，剩下的步骤交给小龙虾来完成。比如这首，适合下雨天宅在家里听的爵士：</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果用户对歌曲有分段落、更加精细化的创作需求，我们另在 Clawhub 也上传 「Music Expert」Skill ，可以对结构化标签进行自动添加，并自动给出不同乐曲段落的方案。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Music Expert：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">clawhub.ai/BLUE-coconut/mm-music-expert</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">除了在 OpenClaw 让你的小龙虾学习这两个 Skill 外，也可以在 MaxClaw 中直接体验，或者在已配对的 IM 软件（飞书、企业微信、钉钉等）中发送 Skill 和指令。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">初次使用，下载对应 skill 的 zip 文件，在 MaxClaw 对话框中上传，通过自然语言沟通，提供 API Key 即可在 MaxClaw 中加载对应能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过指令技巧和参数配置，你的小龙虾也可以绕过传统的文件形式，直接在飞书中以音频消息的形式向你发送内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"word-break: break-all;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">登录 MiniMax 开放平台，注册 API Key：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">platform.minimaxi.com</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Intelligence with Everyone.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562390158172232\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2276\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003828\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93040161&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fq4wL2iaHZfGmXHU4a02nELvm6q34N35cLPb4vTM6VBa1vlnlXe3cPmdAyKd5OvianerQsPib4ExFL2XUqJbHFLSzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "MiniMax 将其语音与音乐模型接口封装至 OpenClaw 生态，使用户能通过 API 调用实现定制化语音回复及多风格音乐创作。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MiniMax 将其语音与音乐模型接口封装至 OpenClaw 生态，使用户能通过 API 调用实现定制化语音回复及多风格音乐创作。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 MiniMax 语音（Speech）和音乐（Music）模型在 OpenClaw 生态中的深度集成方案。通过 Voice Maker 和 Music Maker 两个核心技能，用户可以在飞书、企业微信、钉钉等办公 IM 软件中为 AI 助手（小龙虾）赋予定制化音色，实现多语种、多情感的脚本配音。同时，AI 助手还获得了创作长达 5 分钟完整歌曲、纯音乐及人声哼唱的能力。文章详细展示了如何通过 Clawhub 加载技能、配置 API Key 以及利用自然语言指令进行音频和音乐生成的具体操作流程。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MiniMax 语音与音乐模型接口深度封装并上架 OpenClaw 生态，实现 AI 助手能力升级。",
      "explanation": "通过在 Clawhub 学习新技能，用户可使 AI 助手在飞书、钉钉等平台拥有定制音色和音乐创作能力，显著提升了 IM 场景下的交互维度与趣味性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Voice Maker 技能集成了文字转语音与音色设计功能，支持自然语言描述生成特定音色。",
      "explanation": "该技能内置 40 多种语言和近百种音色，支持自动切分脚本并按情绪匹配输出，能够处理复杂的多角色配音任务，极大降低了专业音频制作的门槛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Music Maker 赋予 AI 助手全能音乐制作能力，支持从纯音乐到带人声歌曲的多种创作模式。",
      "explanation": "用户可以通过简单指令生成长达 5 分钟的流行音乐或白噪音，配合 Music Expert 技能还能进行更精细的结构化标签管理和乐曲段落方案设计。"
    }
  ],
